Titolo: Grand Prix 4

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: Grand Prix 4, commonly known as GP4, was released for the PC on June 21, 2002, and is the last Formula One racing simulator released by the developer Geoff Crammond and the MicroProse label. Based on the 2001 Formula One season, GP4 is a huge graphical and physics upgrade from the previous version, Grand Prix 3 which had been released in 2000.